License: MIT
Description: # Nlpcleaner
        Clean and prepare text for modeling with machine learning.
        - lower all
        - strip all
        - remove numbers
        - remove symbols
        - remove stopwords by detected language
        - lemming or stemming
        
        ## Usage
        
        ```
        from nlpcleaner import Text
        Text(txt).clean()
        ```
        
        ## Tests
        
        ```
        pip install .
        python setup.py test
        ```
        
        ## Push on PyPi
        
        ```
        python setup.py sdist
        pip install twine
        twine upload dist/*
        ```
        
